        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of carpal tunnel syndrome

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy;

          -  Pacemaker or other metallic implants;

          -  Systemic infectious disorders;

          -  Neoplastic disorders;

          -  Epilepsy;

          -  Severe heart disease.

          -  Known hypersensitivity to the components of Xinepa
